Our Story

More than a destination

"We didn't just build a venue we built a lifestyle for Jos. A place where every visit is an unforgettable chapter."

Born from a bold vision by Chief Kefas Ropshik Wungak (Kefiano), Chillers by New Yorker stands as Plateau State's most premium all-in-one hospitality destination. Launched February 2025, redefining what it means to live well in Jos.

Location
No. 1 Breweries Road, Opp. Tamarald Event Center, Jos, Plateau State
Founder & CEO
Chief Kefas Ropshik Wungak (Kefiano) Entrepreneur & Philanthropist
Grand Opening
February 1415, 2025 Featuring Peruzzi, Tekno & Governor Caleb Mutfwang
What We Offer

One Place, Infinite Experiences

From fine dining to late-night entertainment, from poolside relaxation to wellness every desire met.

Restaurant
Continental and local cuisine crafted by expert chefs. Every meal is a celebration of flavour and culture.
Lounge & Nightclub
Jos's premier nightlife experience. World-class DJs, premium spirits, and an atmosphere that electrifies.
Bush Bar
An open-air escape in the heart of Jos. Cold drinks, great company, stars above.
Swimming Pool
A stunning poolside retreat for leisure, day parties and unforgettable weekends.
Chalets & Cabins
Luxurious private chalets for accommodation. Your comfort is our obsession.
Gym & Spa
State-of-the-art gym paired with a rejuvenating spa. Balance performance with serenity.
Premium Bar
From chilled Gulder to bespoke cocktails our bar is stocked for every taste and mood.
24-Hour Supermarket
Everything you need, whenever you need it. Round-the-clock and always stocked.
Sports Viewing
Massive screens, great food, electric crowd. Watch your favourite sports the Chillers way.
